Date: Tue, 9 Jul 2013 20:19:44 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 0610/1115] ARM: dt-bindings: DRA7xx: Specific pinctrl header

The pinctrl IP inside the DRA7XX family differs from what is found on
OMAP2+i which has a 32 bit pin control register. Define a specific header
for DRA7xx pin control.

Signed-off-by: Mugunthan V N <mugunthanvnm@ti.com>
(cherry picked from commit 3c4eb1d2dc0943516dfc39173726df6afa129037)
Signed-off-by: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
---
 include/dt-bindings/pinctrl/dra7xx.h |   48 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 files changed, 48 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 include/dt-bindings/pinctrl/dra7xx.h

diff --git a/include/dt-bindings/pinctrl/dra7xx.h b/include/dt-bindings/pinctrl/dra7xx.h
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..bcd5e4d
--- /dev/null
+++ b/include/dt-bindings/pinctrl/dra7xx.h
@@ -0,0 +1,48 @@
